      <category>后端</category>
      <pubDate>Sun, 03 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h2>前言</h2>
<p>Spring Boot 让 Spring 应用的搭建变得 <strong>极其简单</strong>，通过约定大于配置的理念，开发者可以快速构建生产级别的应用。</p>
<!-- more -->
<h2>一、快速开始</h2>
<h3>1. 创建项目</h3>
<p>推荐使用 <a href="https://start.spring.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Spring Initializr</a> 创建项目，选择以下依赖：</p>
<ul>
<li>Spring Web</li>
<li>Spring Data JPA</li>
<li>MySQL Driver</li>
<li>Lombok</li>
</ul>
<h3>2. 项目结构</h3>
<div class="language- line-numbers-mode" data-highlighter="shiki" data-ext style="--shiki-light:#383A42;--shiki-dark:#abb2bf;--shiki-light-bg:#FAFAFA;--shiki-dark-bg:#282c34"><pre class="shiki shiki-themes one-light one-dark-pro vp-code"><code class="language-"><span class="line"><span>src/</span></span>
